div.p:
In his memorandum, Professor Bergersen classifies the essential points which
                        might be discussed at the suggested meeting under six headings, i.e. 
                            1/

Extension of the whaling season;
                            2/

Fullest possible utilisation of whales taken;
                            3/

Sanctuaries;
                            4/

Size limit for sperm whale;
                            5/

Protection of humpback whales;
                            6/

Limitation of the catch.
